visiblenumbers Django Application
===========================

This is a Django ( 1.5 and 1.4 ) application for [http://www.aastra.com/aastra-6739i.htm](Aastra 6739i Sip Phone) and peoples visual impaired.

Installation
------------

VisibleNumbers require:

* Python 2.7
* Python PIL with TrueType Support
* PhoneNumbers Python Library [https://github.com/daviddrysdale/python-phonenumbers]
* Django 1.4+
* Aastra 6739i SIP device

Usage
------------

Configure the Server IP and the server port on your visiblenumbers installation
Go to settings.py file and put the Server IP and the Server Port ( default : 8000 )
Get the IP of the Aastra 6739i SIP device
Open the Phone web page and go to Advanced Settings -> Action URI
Configure the Incoming Call Action URI with the url of your server installation
Ex: http://<YOUR_IP_SERVER>:8000/visible/aastra?number=$$REMOTENUMBER$$
the $$REMOTENUMBER$$ variable is mandatory

if all is correct call your Extension phone and you can see the result

